<h4 id="1自适应卷积核形状" class="headerLink">
    <a href="#1%e8%87%aa%e9%80%82%e5%ba%94%e5%8d%b7%e7%a7%af%e6%a0%b8%e5%bd%a2%e7%8a%b6" class="header-mark"></a>（1）自适应卷积核形状</h4><div class="code-block highlight is-open show-line-numbers  tw-group tw-my-2">
